{
  "text": "where \u03b8 * p is the polar angle of the daughter proton in the \u039b(\u039b)'s rest frame, \u03b1 H is the hyperon decay parameter (\u03b1 \u039b = \u03b1 \u039b = 0.642 \u00b1 0.013 for \u039b and \u039b), P z is the longitudinal component of Eq. [CITATION_1] .",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "54213333"
